dct_title_s: Map Showing the new Exterior Line on the Atlantic Ocean at East Cape May and Two Mile Beach
dct_description_sm: Map shows the boundaries of Cape May, Wildwood Crest, and Holly Beach. Map also shows various grants along Jarvis Sound. Map covers area from Madison Avenue to the Old Turtle Gut Inlet along the Atlantic Ocean.
